{"tid":1237175,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原稱「騷亂」後改口「暴動」　盧偉聰指自己翻譯不好","createTime":"2019-06-17T14:05:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T14:15:08.000Z","uid":49066,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c884cb4414a01200377c26ffe1131350b70e3348","tid":1237175,"uid":49066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T14:05:03.000Z","msg":"就昨日（12日）大批反對修訂《逃犯條例》草案的示威者佔領金鐘一帶，並於3時開始爆發激烈衝突，警務處處長盧偉聰一度將事件形容為「騷亂」，惟於5時許的新聞稿標題用上「暴動」一詞。盧偉聰於今日（13日）傍晚的記者會表示，澄清當時會見傳媒時因翻譯問題，誤譯成「騷亂」，「其實當時就係指暴動」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">Source: <a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/突發/340385/逃犯條例-原稱-騷亂-後改口-暴動-盧偉聰指自己翻譯不好\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC%2F340385%2F%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E5%8E%9F%E7%A8%B1-%E9%A8%B7%E4%BA%82-%E5%BE%8C%E6%94%B9%E5%8F%A3-%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95-%E7%9B%A7%E5%81%89%E8%81%B0%E6%8C%87%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%BF%BB%E8%AD%AF%E4%B8%8D%E5%A5%BD&d=bJSHN4a6RFajNgW6euKvYRUAsmJrpgm%2FsQZzOZZuI0I%3D&h=99f381ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/突發/340385/逃犯條例-原稱-騷亂-後改口-暴動-盧偉聰指自己翻譯不好</a></span><br />\n<br />\n新聞稿：「警方採取行動制止暴動」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">Source: <a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/app/messages/?press-release&amp;lang=tc&amp;id=P201906130005&amp;fbclid=IwAR17H9tC4b0fD83Gih4ejqxigP2waxIjpOH1pLIZj3BvjQgFn8q7uE2WVOk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Fapp%2Fmessages%2F%3Fpress-release%26lang%3Dtc%26id%3DP201906130005%26fbclid%3DIwAR17H9tC4b0fD83Gih4ejqxigP2waxIjpOH1pLIZj3BvjQgFn8q7uE2WVOk&d=bJSHN4a6RFajNgW6euKvYRUAsmJrpgm%2FsQZzOZZuI0I%3D&h=be5c6a88\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/app/messages/?press-release&amp;lang=tc&amp;id=P201906130005&amp;fbclid=IwAR17H9tC4b0fD83Gih4ejqxigP2waxIjpOH1pLIZj3BvjQgFn8q7uE2WVOk</a></span><br />\n<br />\n而家話只有少範圍果5個人先係暴動？<br />\n<br />\n作為警務處處長可以咁撚兒戲，係度彈出彈入？<br />\n我屌你老母盧偉聰"},{"pid":"a443961b83296dbb41dca8a33a39d3c5b04afbb4","tid":1237175,"uid":